  QuestID: Quest4
  QuestName: Aluna's Stew
  LevelRequirment: 0
  Instructions: Kaleo said he'd bring me Coconut Sprouts himself, but he seemed...
    nervous about it? Is he scared of the Coconuts? Ha! Anyway, I'm making a special
    stew and I could really use some. Would you be able to grab some for me? There
    are Coconuts outside of town to the east. Bring me back 4, that should be more
    than enough!
  Deliver: Oh these are perfect, thank you! My stew is going to be delicious! Here,
    take this you earned it.
